# Title: Sudo Command Execution Monitoring
# ID: 9e9b9e92-8c5d-4d9f-af5b-2g4d5e6f8b8c
# Description: Monitors sudo command executions from system logs
# Level: low
# Author: Thimoté Fétu
# Date: 2026/02/25
# Tags: attack.privilege_escalation, attack.t1548.003
# Index: *_linux
#
# Splunk Query:
index=*_linux message=*sudo* message=*COMMAND=* NOT ((message=*package update* OR message=*systemctl*))
